      "raw_text": "The Northern Pacific lunch room,\nwhich is nearing completion, will\nprobably be ready for occupancy the\nlatter part of January. 1t should be\na wonderful improvement on the pres\nent quarters right in the main depot\n\n\nContractor Deets has the job in hand\nand is doing excellent work The\nnew addition is about 40x60 feet in\nsize. of red brick and stone, two\nstries high."
